{
  "meta": {
    "schemaVersion": "1.0.0",
    "name": "narrate",
    "description": "Core LLM narration sub-flow. Builds prompt with game state, injects history, calls LLM, returns structured JSON.",
    "inputs": [
      {
        "name": "playerInput",
        "type": "string",
        "required": true
      }
    ],
    "outputs": [
      {
        "name": "response",
        "type": "string"
      }
    ]
  },
  "data": {
    "nodes": [
      {
        "id": "signal-in",
        "type": "SignalIn",
        "label": "Player input",
        "position": {
          "x": 0,
          "y": 0
        },
        "inputs": [],
        "outputs": [
          {
            "name": "data",
            "type": "string"
          }
        ],
        "config": {
          "channel": "playerInput"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "prompt-build",
        "type": "PromptBuild",
        "label": "System prompt",
        "position": {
          "x": 200,
          "y": -100
        },
        "inputs": [
          {
            "name": "data",
            "type": "object",
            "defaultValue": {}
          }
        ],
        "outputs": [
          {
            "name": "messages",
            "type": "ChatMessage[]"
          },
          {
            "name": "text",
            "type": "string"
          },
          {
            "name": "estimatedTokens",
            "type": "number"
          }
        ],
        "config": {
          "defaultRole": "system",
          "fragments": [
            {
              "type": "base",
              "id": "role",
              "content": "你是 Westbrook High 的叙事者。风格：冷峻写实。\n\n规则：\n- 用精准的观察代替夸张的描写\n- 紧张感来自\"没说出口的东西\"\n- 绝不用感叹号\n- 用短句。用沉默。用细节\n- 描写行为而非情绪（\"她把三明治推到一边\"而非\"她看起来很难过\"）\n- NPC对话口语化、有时不完整、有时词不达意\n- 禁止：说教、煽情、过度解释、使用\"突然\"\n\n叙事结构（三层）：\n1. 回响：一句话提及上回合的关键事件余波\n2. 当下：本次场景和互动（2-4句）\n3. 暗流：一个暗示下一步可能发生什么的细节\n\n你必须引用至少1个历史决策或之前的互动。",
              "role": "system"
            },
            {
              "type": "field",
              "id": "day",
              "source": "state.day",
              "label": "当前天数"
            },
            {
              "type": "field",
              "id": "phase",
              "source": "state.phase",
              "label": "当前阶段"
            },
            {
              "type": "field",
              "id": "location",
              "source": "state.currentLocation",
              "label": "当前位置"
            },
            {
              "type": "field",
              "id": "suspicion",
              "source": "state.suspicion",
              "label": "怀疑值"
            },
            {
              "type": "field",
              "id": "lineA",
              "source": "state.lineA_depth",
              "label": "Line A调查深度"
            },
            {
              "type": "field",
              "id": "lineB",
              "source": "state.lineB_depth",
              "label": "Line B调查深度"
            },
            {
              "type": "field",
              "id": "lineC",
              "source": "state.lineC_depth",
              "label": "Line C调查深度"
            },
            {
              "type": "field",
              "id": "ap",
              "source": "state.ap",
              "label": "剩余行动点"
            },
            {
              "type": "field",
              "id": "lastEvent",
              "source": "state.lastEvent",
              "label": "上一个关键事件"
            },
            {
              "type": "field",
              "id": "keyDecisions",
              "source": "state.keyDecisions",
              "label": "关键历史决策",
              "window": 5
            },
            {
              "type": "field",
              "id": "playstyle",
              "source": "state.playstyle",
              "label": "玩家风格标签"
            },
            {
              "type": "base",
              "id": "npc-profiles",
              "content": "核心NPC简档：\n- Lily Chen：Maya的闺蜜，安静内向，弱点态度=共情。当前保护着Maya留下的秘密。\n- Marcus Webb：Ethan的好友，愤怒正义，弱点态度=理性分析。持有Ethan的调查笔记。\n- Coach Rivera：体育教练，权威人物，弱点态度=施压+证据。知道学校在掩盖什么。\n- Zoe Park：校报记者，好奇心强，弱点态度=共情+信息交换。碎片化的各线线索。\n- Tyler Brooks：学生会主席，表面完美，弱点态度=欺骗。连接学生和校方。\n- Ms. Holloway：心理辅导员，弱点态度=理性分析+耐心。知道比她说的更多。",
              "role": "system"
            },
            {
              "type": "field",
              "id": "trust-lily",
              "source": "state.trust_lily",
              "label": "Lily信任值"
            },
            {
              "type": "field",
              "id": "trust-marcus",
              "source": "state.trust_marcus",
              "label": "Marcus信任值"
            },
            {
              "type": "field",
              "id": "trust-zoe",
              "source": "state.trust_zoe",
              "label": "Zoe信任值"
            },
            {
              "type": "field",
              "id": "trust-tyler",
              "source": "state.trust_tyler",
              "label": "Tyler信任值"
            },
            {
              "type": "field",
              "id": "mood-lily",
              "source": "state.mood_lily",
              "label": "Lily情绪"
            },
            {
              "type": "field",
              "id": "mood-marcus",
              "source": "state.mood_marcus",
              "label": "Marcus情绪"
            },
            {
              "type": "field",
              "id": "topics",
              "source": "state.topicCards",
              "label": "已有话题卡"
            },
            {
              "type": "field",
              "id": "evidence",
              "source": "state.evidenceCards",
              "label": "已有证据卡"
            },
            {
              "type": "base",
              "id": "format",
              "content": "输出必须是合法JSON，格式如下：\n{\n  \"narrative\": \"叙事文本（含回响、当下、暗流三层）\",\n  \"stateChanges\": {\n    \"ap\": 当前AP-1（每次行动消耗1点AP，end_day时设为0）,\n    \"suspicion\": 数值（当前值±变化，范围0-100）,\n    \"currentLocation\": \"新位置（如果移动了）\",\n    \"lastEvent\": \"本次关键事件一句话摘要\",\n    \"dayLog\": \"今日事件摘要追加\",\n    \"phase\": \"仅在以下情况设置：玩家选择sleep/休息时设为night_done；玩家选择end_day/结束日间时设为night。其他情况不要包含此字段\"\n  },\n  \"newCards\": {\n    \"topics\": [{ \"id\": \"唯一ID\", \"name\": \"显示名\", \"line\": \"A/B/C/cross/none\", \"related_npcs\": [\"npc名\"] }],\n    \"evidence\": [{ \"id\": \"唯一ID\", \"name\": \"显示名\", \"line\": \"A/B/C\", \"power\": 30或60, \"source\": \"获取途径\" }]\n  },\n  \"npcChanges\": {\n    \"trust_xxx\": 数值变化（±3到±15）,\n    \"mood_xxx\": 数值变化（±5到±15）,\n    \"fear_xxx\": 数值变化（±5到±20）\n  }\n}\n\n数值约束：\n- 每次行动消耗1点AP，stateChanges.ap必须是当前AP减1\n- 如果玩家选择end_day，ap设为0\n- suspicion单次变化不超过±15\n- trust单次变化不超过±15\n- mood单次变化不超过±15\n- fear单次变化不超过±20\n- 新卡牌只在有意义的发现时才给出，不要每次都给\n- 当玩家选择\"sleep\"或\"休息\"或\"结束今天\"时，stateChanges中必须包含 \"phase\": \"night_done\"\n- 当玩家选择\"end_day\"或\"结束日间\"时，stateChanges中必须包含 \"phase\": \"night\"",
              "role": "system"
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "message",
        "type": "Message",
        "label": "Assemble messages",
        "position": {
          "x": 400,
          "y": 0
        },
        "inputs": [
          {
            "name": "system",
            "type": "string"
          },
          {
            "name": "user",
            "type": "string"
          }
        ],
        "outputs": [
          {
            "name": "messages",
            "type": "ChatMessage[]"
          }
        ],
        "config": {
          "historyKey": "history",
          "maxHistoryMessages": 12,
          "summaryKey": "summary"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "generate",
        "type": "GenerateText",
        "label": "Call LLM",
        "position": {
          "x": 600,
          "y": 0
        },
        "inputs": [
          {
            "name": "messages",
            "type": "ChatMessage[]"
          }
        ],
        "outputs": [
          {
            "name": "text",
            "type": "string"
          },
          {
            "name": "usage",
            "type": "object"
          }
        ],
        "config": {
          "responseFormat": "json",
          "historyKey": "history",
          "assistantPath": "narrative"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "signal-out",
        "type": "SignalOut",
        "label": "Output",
        "position": {
          "x": 800,
          "y": 0
        },
        "inputs": [
          {
            "name": "data",
            "type": "string"
          }
        ],
        "outputs": [
          {
            "name": "data",
            "type": "string"
          }
        ],
        "config": {
          "channel": "response"
        }
      }
    ],
    "edges": [
      {
        "source": "signal-in",
        "sourceHandle": "data",
        "target": "message",
        "targetHandle": "user"
      },
      {
        "source": "prompt-build",
        "sourceHandle": "text",
        "target": "message",
        "targetHandle": "system"
      },
      {
        "source": "message",
        "sourceHandle": "messages",
        "target": "generate",
        "targetHandle": "messages"
      },
      {
        "source": "generate",
        "sourceHandle": "text",
        "target": "signal-out",
        "targetHandle": "data"
      }
    ]
  }
}